		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Talked to Quietust and did some more tracing in visual 2c02, and it looks like the secondary OAM clear and sprite evaluation is skipped on the pre-render line. Updating the <span class="posthilit">diagram</span> to reflect this.<br /><br />This might also mean that it's possible for sprites to affect the rendering of the first scanline somehow.

		
