	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Author:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>beannaich</b> [ Thu Mar 14, 2013 12:10 am ]</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Feedback wanted on SVG PPU frame timing <span class="posthilit">diagram</span></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Plazm wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent"><div class="quotetitle">beannaich wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Of these 34 fetches, only 33 are ever actually used in rendering</div><br />Why 33? (in line 32 tiles)</div><br /><br />To allow for fine horizontal scrolling. ((256 pixels + 8 pixel fine scroll) / 8 pixels per tile) = 33 tiles.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


